1
00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:03,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="18"><font color="#7e7b61">Tips from Makio-chan</font></font></font></font>

2
00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:03,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="14"><font color="#7e7b61">Vocab</font></font></font></font>

3
00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:03,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="14"><font color="#7e7b61">Pick a main theme</font></font></font></font>

4
00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:03,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="14"><font color="#7e7b61">Focus on what I want to say most</font></font></font></font>

5
00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:03,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="16"><font color="#7e7b61">Write with
 the intent to kill</font></font></font></font>

6
00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:03,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="10"><font color="#7e7b61">Sounds scary</font></font></font></font>

7
00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:03,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="12"><font color="#7e7b61">What do I want to say?</font></font></font></font>

8
00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:03,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="12"><font color="#7e7b61">I don't have anything to say...</font></font></font></font>

9
00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:03,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#7e7b61">Nothing to say</font></font></font>

10
00:00:04,550 --> 00:00:05,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have things settled down?</font>

11
00:00:05,940 --> 00:00:08,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Yeah, for now.</i></font>

12
00:00:08,380 --> 00:00:10,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Glad to hear it.</font>

13
00:00:10,020 --> 00:00:11,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Yeah, I guess.</i></font>

14
00:00:10,030 --> 00:00:17,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="16">{\an8}<b><font color="#f5f5f6">Kasamachi</font></b></font></font></font>

15
00:00:14,080 --> 00:00:16,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Actually, can I vent for a bit?</i></font>

16
00:00:16,270 --> 00:00:17,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's rare for you.</font>

17
00:00:17,780 --> 00:00:21,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've learned it's not 
always bad to complain.</font>

18
00:00:22,340 --> 00:00:23,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Go ahead.</i></font>

19
00:00:23,650 --> 00:00:26,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have to admit I was 
shocked when I first heard</font>

20
00:00:26,180 --> 00:00:29,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that my stubborn old man
 was in the hospital.</font>

21
00:00:29,040 --> 00:00:31,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But what's been the biggest headache</font>

22
00:00:31,840 --> 00:00:35,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is his damn attitude toward 
the hospital staff.</font>

23
00:00:35,540 --> 00:00:36,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's a strong tone!</i></font>

24
00:00:36,970 --> 00:00:38,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Are you good?</i></font>

25
00:00:38,050 --> 00:00:40,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't someone going to hear you?</font>

26
00:00:40,020 --> 00:00:42,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's fine. I'm outside right now.</i></font>

27
00:00:42,730 --> 00:00:45,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But man, I hope I don't 
turn out like that.</i></font>

28
00:00:45,640 --> 00:00:48,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With the nurse,
 he was all like, "Hey, you!"</font>

29
00:00:48,800 --> 00:00:51,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who knew he'd be this bad
 even on his sickness?</font>

30
00:00:51,200 --> 00:00:53,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I seriously couldn't believe it.</i></font>

31
00:00:53,510 --> 00:00:54,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hear you.</font>

32
00:00:55,120 --> 00:00:58,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Well, I suppose it means 
he's well enough to be rude.</i></font>

33
00:00:58,560 --> 00:00:59,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kasamachi-kun.</font>

34
00:00:59,840 --> 00:01:00,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Yeah?</i></font>

35
00:01:00,830 --> 00:01:05,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It might take time, but I hope 
you break free of that curse.</i></font>

36
00:01:07,300 --> 00:01:08,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You and me both.</font>

37
00:01:09,140 --> 00:01:12,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Although I'd say you're
 further along than I am.</i></font>

38
00:01:12,190 --> 00:01:16,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Well, you learn to pass down 
the good and get rid of the bad.</font>

39
00:01:14,270 --> 00:01:15,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i><i>Curse...</i></i></font>

40
00:01:16,090 --> 00:01:17,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="36"><font color="#7e7a63">Curse</font></font></font></font>

41
00:01:16,850 --> 00:01:18,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>C-u-r...</i></font>

42
00:01:27,980 --> 00:01:34,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Georgia"><font size="18"><font color="#3b3132">Journal with Witch</font></font></font></font>

43
00:02:55,110 --> 00:03:00,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="12"><font face="Georgia">{\an3}<font color="#ffffff">Episode 10\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h<font size="18">Bind</font></font></font></font></font>

44
00:02:57,040 --> 00:02:59,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Emiri, do you want soup too?</font>

45
00:02:59,110 --> 00:03:01,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Yeah, but I don't need toast.</font>

46
00:03:02,750 --> 00:03:04,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here, take it to the table yourself.</font>

47
00:03:04,400 --> 00:03:06,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're a high schooler now.</font>

48
00:03:06,410 --> 00:03:07,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

49
00:03:07,480 --> 00:03:09,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Put the paper down, darling.</font>

50
00:03:09,400 --> 00:03:10,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right.</font>

51
00:03:13,210 --> 00:03:15,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Emiri, don't forget your lunch.</font>

52
00:03:16,140 --> 00:03:17,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

53
00:03:17,670 --> 00:03:21,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Makio-san told me she was having 
a hard time making bento boxes.</font>

54
00:03:19,970 --> 00:03:23,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Kojima-san is actually a scientist!</i></font>

55
00:03:21,430 --> 00:03:24,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder if novelists have 
to pull all-nighters.</font>

56
00:03:23,830 --> 00:03:28,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Someone that pretty works in science?</i></font>

57
00:03:24,570 --> 00:03:26,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I dunno.</font>

58
00:03:26,100 --> 00:03:30,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's funny, 'cause last time I went 
over there, she was day drinking.</font>

59
00:03:28,520 --> 00:03:32,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Her dress underneath the 
white coat is a nice sight.</i></font>

60
00:03:30,180 --> 00:03:32,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really? I wish I could do that too.</font>

61
00:03:32,340 --> 00:03:34,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}What are you talking about?</i></font>

62
00:03:33,680 --> 00:03:36,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's considered sexual harassment 
in this day and age.</font>

63
00:03:34,690 --> 00:03:39,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}She's shared some other photos 
with us for our viewers.</i></font>

64
00:03:37,080 --> 00:03:40,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd say that comment itself is harassment.</font>

65
00:03:40,020 --> 00:03:40,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

66
00:03:40,690 --> 00:03:42,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Always has been.</font>

67
00:03:41,340 --> 00:03:45,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Kojima-san is sharing her life as a 
woman in science on social media...</i></font>

68
00:03:42,420 --> 00:03:44,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh... Right.</font>

69
00:03:48,040 --> 00:03:50,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The same route to school as always.</i></font>

70
00:03:50,920 --> 00:03:54,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Crowds of people. Children running.</i></font>

71
00:03:54,720 --> 00:03:56,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>White breath.</i></font>

72
00:03:56,830 --> 00:04:00,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Vending machines with cocoa and...</i></font>

73
00:03:57,960 --> 00:04:00,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial Black"><font size="14"><font color="#e4d8c8">Milk Cocoa</font></font></font></font>

74
00:03:57,960 --> 00:04:00,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial Black"><font size="14"><font color="#e4d8c8">Milk Cocoa</font></font></font></font>

75
00:04:00,960 --> 00:04:03,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia"><b><font size="20">{\an3}<font color="#f3f2f2">Hey, let's go skiing.</font></font></b></font></font>

76
00:04:00,960 --> 00:04:03,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia"><b><font size="22">{\an3}<font color="#f3f2f2">Hey, let's go skiing.</font></font></b></font></font>

77
00:04:01,690 --> 00:04:03,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A poster's smile.</i></font>

78
00:04:04,320 --> 00:04:07,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Um... Bicycles. Trains.</i></font>

79
00:04:07,970 --> 00:04:10,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>"S" for... school field trip.</i></font>

80
00:04:10,970 --> 00:04:13,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>"P" for... puffs of cloud.</i></font>

81
00:04:13,260 --> 00:04:15,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>"D" for... dwarf flying squirrel?</i></font>

82
00:04:16,170 --> 00:04:18,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>"L" for lines of trees along traffic.</i></font>

83
00:04:18,020 --> 00:04:19,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>"C" for...</i></font>

84
00:04:21,130 --> 00:04:22,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Curse.</i></font>

85
00:04:23,680 --> 00:04:25,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>How did that turn into a word chain game?</i></font>

86
00:04:30,440 --> 00:04:31,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Emi—</font>

87
00:04:30,680 --> 00:04:31,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Emiri!</font>

88
00:04:34,310 --> 00:04:37,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, Chicchi!</font>

89
00:04:37,100 --> 00:04:38,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, and Asa.</font>

90
00:04:38,790 --> 00:04:40,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Chicchi"?</font>

91
00:04:41,510 --> 00:04:44,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Chiyo-chicchi and I have 
chemistry together.</font>

92
00:04:44,640 --> 00:04:46,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh.</font>

93
00:04:46,010 --> 00:04:49,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Emiri and I are gonna be pals 
in the science track next year.</font>

94
00:04:49,600 --> 00:04:51,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pals?</font>

95
00:04:51,280 --> 00:04:54,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, you're choosing the science track?</font>

96
00:04:54,010 --> 00:04:55,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess so after all.</font>

97
00:04:55,630 --> 00:04:57,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And the way she says your name...</font>

98
00:04:57,340 --> 00:04:58,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, like the English "Emily."</font>

99
00:04:58,960 --> 00:05:01,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been asking Chicchi for advice 
since she's doing science.</font>

100
00:05:01,900 --> 00:05:04,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, I'm gonna be a doctor.</font>

101
00:05:04,650 --> 00:05:05,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow.</font>

102
00:05:05,790 --> 00:05:08,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Since both my parents are doctors and all.</font>

103
00:05:08,150 --> 00:05:09,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't that awesome?</font>

104
00:05:09,750 --> 00:05:12,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not sure how I feel about following
in their footsteps, though.</font>

105
00:05:13,170 --> 00:05:14,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Catch you later.</font>

106
00:05:14,730 --> 00:05:16,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Morning, Sakura!</font>

107
00:05:16,600 --> 00:05:17,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Morning!</font>

108
00:05:17,990 --> 00:05:21,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, did you hear 
about the pop quiz in math?</font>

109
00:05:21,520 --> 00:05:23,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not a pop quiz.
They told us last year.</font>

110
00:05:23,400 --> 00:05:26,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? I totally missed that!</font>

111
00:05:27,410 --> 00:05:30,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, first-years!
 Run like your life's on the line!</font>

112
00:05:32,030 --> 00:05:34,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yoshimura, pick up the pace!</font>

113
00:05:34,540 --> 00:05:35,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Roger that!</font>

114
00:05:36,090 --> 00:05:39,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Run for your life. 
Run, baseball team, run.</i></font>

115
00:05:41,190 --> 00:05:42,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? No way.</font>

116
00:05:42,900 --> 00:05:44,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For how long?</font>

117
00:05:44,380 --> 00:05:45,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, there she is.</font>

118
00:05:46,190 --> 00:05:47,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get a load of this.</font>

119
00:05:48,300 --> 00:05:51,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Apparently Shinozaki's 
going out with Hashiba!</font>

120
00:05:51,140 --> 00:05:52,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can you believe him?</font>

121
00:05:52,540 --> 00:05:53,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cool.</font>

122
00:05:53,510 --> 00:05:55,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's with that reaction?</font>

123
00:05:55,370 --> 00:05:57,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I don't really care.</font>

124
00:05:57,210 --> 00:05:59,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But he tried so hard to get with you!</font>

125
00:05:59,710 --> 00:06:01,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you think it's way too soon?</font>

126
00:06:01,350 --> 00:06:04,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's fine. It's not like I like him.</font>

127
00:06:05,610 --> 00:06:07,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dang. She's too good for him.</font>

128
00:06:07,960 --> 00:06:09,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shut up.</font>

129
00:06:09,060 --> 00:06:11,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Class is starting. Get in your seats.</font>

130
00:06:12,140 --> 00:06:18,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"What happiness to sit in intimate 
conversation with someone of like mind,</font>

131
00:06:18,200 --> 00:06:24,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">warmed by candid discussion of the 
amusing and fleeting ways of this world...</font>

132
00:06:24,350 --> 00:06:28,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But such a friend is hard to find, 
and instead you sit there doing your best</font>

133
00:06:28,410 --> 00:06:31,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to fit in with whatever the other 
is saying, feeling deeply alone."</font>

134
00:06:34,740 --> 00:06:38,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take note from Morimoto 
and remember to review your exercises.</font>

135
00:06:35,890 --> 00:06:37,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Great job.</font>

136
00:06:37,240 --> 00:06:39,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}We covered this in class.</font>

137
00:06:38,200 --> 00:06:40,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}We'll have end-of-term exams next month.</font>

138
00:06:38,200 --> 00:06:39,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Someone on the science track.</i></font>

139
00:06:40,430 --> 00:06:42,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>With a perfect score on her quiz.</i></font>

140
00:06:40,580 --> 00:06:42,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Okay, get your textbooks out.</font>

141
00:06:42,490 --> 00:06:44,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Let's move on to today's lesson.</font>

142
00:06:42,940 --> 00:06:45,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Cloudy skies are a pest.</i></font>

143
00:06:44,080 --> 00:06:45,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Starting on page 234...</font>

144
00:06:46,520 --> 00:06:48,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How did you do on the quiz?</font>

145
00:06:48,830 --> 00:06:51,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bombed it. I didn't study at all.</font>

146
00:06:51,820 --> 00:06:53,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Neither did I.</font>

147
00:07:01,020 --> 00:07:03,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="18"><font color="#75725a">November 27th</font></font></font></font>

148
00:07:01,020 --> 00:07:03,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="16"><font color="#75725a">Juno-san</font></font></font></font>

149
00:07:01,020 --> 00:07:03,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="18"><font color="#75725a">I want to become the person I want to be!</font></font></font></font>

150
00:07:06,780 --> 00:07:12,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#75725a">November 27th</font></font></font>

151
00:07:06,780 --> 00:07:12,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#75725a">Juno-san</font></font></font>

152
00:07:06,780 --> 00:07:12,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#625f4c">I want to become the person I want to be!</font></font></font>

153
00:07:08,120 --> 00:07:11,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I want to become the person I want to be!
I want to become the person I want to be!</i></font>

154
00:07:11,750 --> 00:07:12,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I want to become the pers—</i></font>

155
00:07:18,530 --> 00:07:19,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

156
00:07:19,460 --> 00:07:20,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really?</font>

157
00:07:21,040 --> 00:07:24,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh... Wait, what day is it?</font>

158
00:07:24,030 --> 00:07:25,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm home.</font>

159
00:07:25,380 --> 00:07:27,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh. Right.</font>

160
00:07:27,550 --> 00:07:29,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>"Welcome home."</i></font>

161
00:07:29,720 --> 00:07:31,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Never mind that.</font>

162
00:07:31,290 --> 00:07:33,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, what day will that be?</font>

163
00:07:34,810 --> 00:07:37,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? No, I don't remember.</font>

164
00:07:39,000 --> 00:07:40,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't intend to.</font>

165
00:07:42,530 --> 00:07:45,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right. I'll ask her.</font>

166
00:07:45,270 --> 00:07:46,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, she comes first.</font>

167
00:07:46,840 --> 00:07:47,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

168
00:07:48,570 --> 00:07:50,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Arial"><font size="12"><b><font color="#e5ecec">Mom</font></b></font></font></font>

169
00:07:54,250 --> 00:07:56,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, listen...</font>

170
00:07:56,320 --> 00:07:57,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm home.</font>

171
00:07:57,590 --> 00:07:59,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, yeah, welcome back.</font>

172
00:07:59,410 --> 00:08:01,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, it's almost—</font>

173
00:08:03,810 --> 00:08:06,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, that reminds me.</font>

174
00:08:06,420 --> 00:08:07,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? What?</font>

175
00:08:08,170 --> 00:08:11,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When's your birthday?</font>

176
00:08:11,370 --> 00:08:13,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">September 4th.</font>

177
00:08:17,260 --> 00:08:20,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, I totally screwed that up.</font>

178
00:08:20,520 --> 00:08:23,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, you didn't seem
 to celebrate yours either.</font>

179
00:08:23,370 --> 00:08:26,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I just figured birthdays 
weren't a thing here.</font>

180
00:08:26,590 --> 00:08:28,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not like that's a rule or anything.</font>

181
00:08:28,910 --> 00:08:31,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And never you mind about my birthday.</font>

182
00:08:31,350 --> 00:08:35,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Adults have enough reasons 
to get together to eat and drink.</font>

183
00:08:36,440 --> 00:08:38,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry. We'll celebrate this year.</font>

184
00:08:38,980 --> 00:08:40,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">On both of our birthdays.</font>

185
00:08:40,750 --> 00:08:42,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, okay.</font>

186
00:08:42,250 --> 00:08:45,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And to make up for missing 
your last birthday,</font>

187
00:08:45,850 --> 00:08:49,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we'll have a little party 
to celebrate our first year together.</font>

188
00:08:49,980 --> 00:08:52,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow! Okay.</font>

189
00:08:53,370 --> 00:08:55,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Also, one more thing...</font>

190
00:08:55,740 --> 00:08:57,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I meant to talk to you about this.</font>

191
00:08:58,100 --> 00:09:02,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're coming up on the anniversary
of your parents' death.</font>

192
00:09:04,240 --> 00:09:09,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you want to do something for it,
we'll fit that in too.</font>

193
00:09:09,620 --> 00:09:11,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do something for it?</font>

194
00:09:11,590 --> 00:09:12,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Could be anything.</font>

195
00:09:13,140 --> 00:09:17,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can visit their grave 
or have a monk come over.</font>

196
00:09:17,040 --> 00:09:21,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Something typical like that,</font>

197
00:09:21,040 --> 00:09:24,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">or, if you want, maybe talking 
to me or someone else.</font>

198
00:09:24,500 --> 00:09:26,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whatever you'd like.</font>

199
00:09:26,640 --> 00:09:30,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course, doing nothing 
is also an option.</font>

200
00:09:30,790 --> 00:09:32,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just think about it.</font>

201
00:09:32,240 --> 00:09:33,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And let me know anytime.</font>

202
00:09:34,140 --> 00:09:35,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

203
00:09:38,340 --> 00:09:41,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for today, Juno-san. I had fun.</font>

204
00:09:41,930 --> 00:09:44,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad you could blow off some steam.</font>

205
00:09:44,680 --> 00:09:47,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I bet it's tough to welcome 
a kid out of the blue.</font>

206
00:09:47,740 --> 00:09:49,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, I guess.</font>

207
00:09:49,630 --> 00:09:52,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She kind of reminds me 
of a dog. Like a shiba.</font>

208
00:09:52,400 --> 00:09:55,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're not the first to say so. 
Maybe it's her eyes.</font>

209
00:09:57,640 --> 00:10:01,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, until she goes to college 
or legally becomes an adult...</font>

210
00:10:01,950 --> 00:10:03,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I figure I'll do my best until then.</font>

211
00:10:04,160 --> 00:10:06,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So just a few more years.</font>

212
00:10:08,200 --> 00:10:11,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know about that, Koudai-san.</font>

213
00:10:13,260 --> 00:10:20,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm a grand old adult myself, but I'm 
still just a kid in front of my mom.</font>

214
00:10:20,660 --> 00:10:22,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The same will go for her.</font>

215
00:10:22,500 --> 00:10:27,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, I know in your case,
you're not mother and daughter by blood.</font>

216
00:10:28,350 --> 00:10:32,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But still, I expect there'll be something.</font>

217
00:10:32,970 --> 00:10:35,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even into adulthood.</font>

218
00:10:35,240 --> 00:10:37,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Probably forever.</font>

219
00:10:39,360 --> 00:10:41,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You made a deal with the devil.</font>

220
00:10:41,740 --> 00:10:43,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That makes it sound bad, but...</font>

221
00:10:44,530 --> 00:10:47,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no "until so and so"
 or "until this is over."</font>

222
00:10:48,080 --> 00:10:52,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't think that's something
you ever get to cut completely off.</font>

223
00:10:54,260 --> 00:10:55,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah...</font>

224
00:10:56,900 --> 00:10:58,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're right.</font>

225
00:10:58,290 --> 00:10:59,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know I am.</font>

226
00:11:02,830 --> 00:11:06,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, that's right. 
I have a favor to ask of you.</font>

227
00:11:06,770 --> 00:11:09,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? You're freaking me out.</font>

228
00:11:09,330 --> 00:11:13,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Remember that old picture of yours
you showed me before?</font>

229
00:11:13,380 --> 00:11:15,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can you send it to me?</font>

230
00:11:15,260 --> 00:11:17,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Why?!</font>

231
00:11:17,370 --> 00:11:20,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's my favorite. Please!</font>

232
00:11:20,280 --> 00:11:23,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To help me get out of my rut! Come on!</font>

233
00:11:23,250 --> 00:11:25,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That has nothing to do 
with writer's block!</font>

234
00:11:25,860 --> 00:11:28,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not doing it!</font>

235
00:11:27,660 --> 00:11:29,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Please!</font>

236
00:11:31,530 --> 00:11:33,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah, how cute.</font>

237
00:11:33,770 --> 00:11:36,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's going in my favorites.</font>

238
00:11:41,730 --> 00:11:45,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But still, I expect there'll be something.</i></font>

239
00:11:46,240 --> 00:11:48,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even into adulthood.</i></font>

240
00:11:48,770 --> 00:11:51,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Probably forever.</i></font>

241
00:11:51,370 --> 00:11:55,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sis! Mom wants to take a picture of us!</font>

242
00:11:55,230 --> 00:11:57,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Again?</font>

243
00:11:57,310 --> 00:11:58,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hurry!</font>

244
00:11:58,310 --> 00:12:01,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you talking about?
It's been a whole year.</font>

245
00:12:00,530 --> 00:12:02,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Hurry it up, Sis!</font>

246
00:12:01,390 --> 00:12:04,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But Makio always goofs around.</font>

247
00:12:04,070 --> 00:12:05,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't be like that.</font>

248
00:12:05,340 --> 00:12:09,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll be happy to look back 
on these when you grow up.</font>

249
00:12:12,660 --> 00:12:15,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I bet she didn't want to die...</font>

250
00:12:16,060 --> 00:12:19,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia"><font size="18"><font color="#000000">Journal with Witch</font></font></font></font>

251
00:12:23,500 --> 00:12:24,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There she is!</font>

252
00:12:24,920 --> 00:12:28,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Takumi, Takumi, Takumi, Takumi! Big news!</font>

253
00:12:28,610 --> 00:12:30,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's going on?</font>

254
00:12:30,180 --> 00:12:31,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Didn't you hear?</font>

255
00:12:31,090 --> 00:12:33,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The band club is having 
an outdoor concert on campus</font>

256
00:12:33,900 --> 00:12:35,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to welcome the new students in April!</font>

257
00:12:35,820 --> 00:12:37,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh. Where?</font>

258
00:12:37,430 --> 00:12:39,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In the courtyard concourse!</font>

259
00:12:40,040 --> 00:12:41,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow, that's cool.</font>

260
00:12:41,910 --> 00:12:43,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, that's not the point.</font>

261
00:12:43,340 --> 00:12:46,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're picking the lead 
vocalist by audition!</font>

262
00:12:46,860 --> 00:12:48,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh...</font>

263
00:12:48,580 --> 00:12:49,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello?</font>

264
00:12:49,990 --> 00:12:52,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're all talking about auditioning!</font>

265
00:12:52,450 --> 00:12:54,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's finally our chance to shine!</font>

266
00:12:56,710 --> 00:13:00,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="20"><font color="#493642">New Club Captain   Second-Year Misaki Oki</font></font></font></font>

267
00:12:56,710 --> 00:12:57,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}What's the harm?</font>

268
00:12:57,890 --> 00:12:59,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}We're only playing
with one acoustic guitar.</font>

269
00:12:59,970 --> 00:13:04,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Let's kick off the new term
 by switching things up.</font>

270
00:13:06,450 --> 00:13:09,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}No application requirements!</font>

271
00:13:09,450 --> 00:13:11,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But what about lyrics?</font>

272
00:13:11,220 --> 00:13:13,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I haven't been able to write 
an original song yet.</font>

273
00:13:13,670 --> 00:13:15,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't need any!</font>

274
00:13:15,050 --> 00:13:16,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can audition with any song.</font>

275
00:13:16,600 --> 00:13:19,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's show 'em our chops, Takumi!</font>

276
00:13:19,400 --> 00:13:21,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you say, Asa-chan?</font>

277
00:13:26,670 --> 00:13:31,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, what if we try writing 
our own original songs?</font>

278
00:13:32,230 --> 00:13:34,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you being serious?</font>

279
00:13:34,840 --> 00:13:38,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure am. I don't want to be a 
face in the crowd forever.</font>

280
00:13:38,900 --> 00:13:40,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Original songs, huh?</font>

281
00:13:41,710 --> 00:13:44,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-Then I'll come up with the lyrics!</font>

282
00:13:45,330 --> 00:13:49,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't write any melodies, 
but I think I can manage lyrics.</font>

283
00:13:50,490 --> 00:13:54,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My aunt's a novelist, 
and she says anyone can write.</font>

284
00:13:54,150 --> 00:13:56,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That can't be true.</font>

285
00:13:56,400 --> 00:13:58,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Great! Then I'll give it a shot too.</font>

286
00:13:58,600 --> 00:14:00,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can muster one song
if we work together.</font>

287
00:14:00,540 --> 00:14:03,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, I'll pitch in too. 
Don't leave me out.</font>

288
00:14:04,070 --> 00:14:05,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Perfect. Then it's settled.</font>

289
00:14:06,440 --> 00:14:09,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've got a feeling the tides
 are about to change.</font>

290
00:14:10,060 --> 00:14:10,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

291
00:14:12,730 --> 00:14:13,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's do it.</font>

292
00:14:13,930 --> 00:14:14,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

293
00:14:14,900 --> 00:14:16,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good.</font>

294
00:14:16,030 --> 00:14:17,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We got this!</font>

295
00:14:17,020 --> 00:14:18,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

296
00:14:19,310 --> 00:14:21,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What was all that for, then?</font>

297
00:14:27,550 --> 00:14:29,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="20">{\an1}<font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#41372b">78th Hachioji District Elementary</font></font></font></font>

298
00:14:27,550 --> 00:14:29,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="36"><font face="Arial Black"><font color="#8c8675">Choir Competition</font></font></font></font>

299
00:14:42,290 --> 00:14:43,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Curse...</i></font>

300
00:14:48,820 --> 00:14:51,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so screwed for the mock exams.</font>

301
00:14:51,520 --> 00:14:52,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Same.</font>

302
00:14:52,780 --> 00:14:57,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What difference does it even make
if we can get into a good college?</font>

303
00:14:57,160 --> 00:15:00,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know. It doesn't matter 
how smart girls are.</font>

304
00:15:00,260 --> 00:15:01,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We end up getting married anyway.</font>

305
00:15:01,820 --> 00:15:04,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Makio-san would get riled 
up if she heard that.</i></font>

306
00:15:04,820 --> 00:15:06,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Nah, she'd just ignore it.</i></font>

307
00:15:08,370 --> 00:15:12,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>"It's not even worth 
listening to," she'd say.</i></font>

308
00:15:37,990 --> 00:15:40,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="12">{\an4}<font color="#353332">Asa</font></font></font></font>

309
00:15:43,240 --> 00:15:45,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, Miri-chan!</font>

310
00:15:45,500 --> 00:15:47,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I got stuck doing some paperwork.</font>

311
00:15:49,480 --> 00:15:50,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for waiting.</font>

312
00:15:50,750 --> 00:15:53,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was about to give up and go home.</font>

313
00:15:53,070 --> 00:15:54,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My bad.</font>

314
00:15:55,260 --> 00:15:57,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No way! That's way too strict.</font>

315
00:15:57,530 --> 00:16:00,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's an all-girls schools for you.</font>

316
00:16:01,880 --> 00:16:03,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that your parents?</font>

317
00:16:01,890 --> 00:16:03,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="12">{\an4}<font color="#353332">Asa</font></font></font></font>

318
00:16:01,890 --> 00:16:03,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="12">{\an4}<font color="#353332">Asa</font></font></font></font>

319
00:16:03,880 --> 00:16:07,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, a friend. You know...</font>

320
00:16:07,600 --> 00:16:10,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The childhood friend who lost her parents.</font>

321
00:16:10,500 --> 00:16:11,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh...</font>

322
00:16:12,490 --> 00:16:16,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel so bad for her.
 I can't even imagine.</font>

323
00:16:16,940 --> 00:16:19,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, I don't know...</font>

324
00:16:20,290 --> 00:16:22,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our whole families were close.</font>

325
00:16:23,230 --> 00:16:26,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like, we had sleepovers and stuff.</font>

326
00:16:26,090 --> 00:16:27,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So it was a big shock for me too.</font>

327
00:16:29,190 --> 00:16:32,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It hit hard, but...</font>

328
00:16:32,050 --> 00:16:42,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial">{\an4}<font color="#353332">Asa</font></font></font>

329
00:16:32,050 --> 00:16:35,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font face="Arial"><font size="16"><font color="#484549">Emiri</font></font></font></font>

330
00:16:32,050 --> 00:16:35,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font face="Arial"><font size="16"><font color="#484549">You up?</font></font></font></font>

331
00:16:32,050 --> 00:16:35,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font face="Arial"><font size="16"><font color="#484549">Yeah, I am</font></font></font></font>

332
00:16:32,050 --> 00:16:35,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font face="Arial"><font size="16"><font color="#484549">What's up?</font></font></font></font>

333
00:16:33,390 --> 00:16:34,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know.</font>

334
00:16:34,880 --> 00:16:36,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I couldn't help thinking...</font>

335
00:16:35,050 --> 00:16:37,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font face="Arial"><font size="16"><font color="#484549">I don't know</font></font></font></font>

336
00:16:35,070 --> 00:16:37,070
