<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't that awful?</font>

363
00:16:56,640 --> 00:16:58,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I still think it sometimes.</font>

364
00:16:58,880 --> 00:17:00,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's just a lot.</font>

365
00:17:00,930 --> 00:17:04,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you haven't quit 
being her friend, have you?</font>

366
00:17:04,880 --> 00:17:07,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You haven't quit, Miri-chan.</font>

367
00:17:08,980 --> 00:17:11,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, I don't actually plan to.</font>

368
00:17:11,220 --> 00:17:13,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even though she gets 
on my nerves sometimes.</font>

369
00:17:15,320 --> 00:17:16,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're friends, after all.</font>

370
00:17:17,720 --> 00:17:20,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're kind, Miri-chan.</font>

371
00:17:20,000 --> 00:17:21,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really?</font>

372
00:17:21,730 --> 00:17:23,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, you are.</font>

373
00:17:25,740 --> 00:17:27,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I definitely think so.</font>

374
00:17:28,180 --> 00:17:29,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what I really...</font>

375
00:17:30,830 --> 00:17:31,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">like about you.</font>

376
00:17:35,990 --> 00:17:37,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tell me that more.</font>

377
00:17:38,290 --> 00:17:39,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Won't it get old?</font>

378
00:17:39,970 --> 00:17:41,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that even possible?</font>

379
00:18:10,930 --> 00:18:13,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Emiri's not reading my texts.</font>

380
00:18:14,150 --> 00:18:16,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe she's at cram school.</font>

381
00:18:16,320 --> 00:18:18,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know, but still.</font>

382
00:18:19,290 --> 00:18:22,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why don't you reply to texts, Makio-chan?</font>

383
00:18:23,350 --> 00:18:26,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I only do that sometimes.</font>

384
00:18:26,560 --> 00:18:28,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sometimes I do reply.</font>

385
00:18:28,310 --> 00:18:30,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There you go again...</font>

386
00:18:30,110 --> 00:18:32,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, so why don't you sometimes?</font>

387
00:18:32,600 --> 00:18:34,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why?</font>

388
00:18:34,860 --> 00:18:38,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I need to protect my peace 
and quiet sometimes.</font>

389
00:18:38,180 --> 00:18:40,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your peace and quiet?</font>

390
00:18:40,000 --> 00:18:40,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yup.</font>

391
00:18:41,470 --> 00:18:44,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't that lonely, though?</font>

392
00:18:44,770 --> 00:18:47,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure it's not for you, but...</font>

393
00:18:47,810 --> 00:18:49,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font color="#595443"><b>Quiet</b></font></font></font>

394
00:18:48,130 --> 00:18:49,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're starting to get it.</font>

395
00:18:49,820 --> 00:18:51,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not really.</font>

396
00:18:51,810 --> 00:18:54,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font color="#595443"><b>Quietness</b></font></font></font>

397
00:18:51,810 --> 00:18:54,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="20"><font face="Arial"><font color="#595443"><b>Lonely</b></font></font></font></font>

398
00:18:55,920 --> 00:18:59,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that kind of like the desert?</font>

399
00:18:59,520 --> 00:19:02,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure that depends on the person.</font>

400
00:19:02,870 --> 00:19:08,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It could be a grassy field, a forest, 
a mountain, or even the beach.</font>

401
00:19:08,390 --> 00:19:09,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh...</font>

