<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="20">{\an1}<font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#41372b">78th Hachioji District Elementary</font></font></font></font>

411
00:19:24,220 --> 00:19:27,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="36"><font face="Arial Black"><font color="#8c8675">Choir Competition</font></font></font></font>

412
00:19:30,380 --> 00:19:33,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good job. How was it?</font>

413
00:19:33,100 --> 00:19:34,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I had fun!</font>

414
00:19:35,120 --> 00:19:37,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's too bad you didn't win.</font>

415
00:19:37,900 --> 00:19:42,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? I didn't really care about winning.</font>

416
00:19:42,020 --> 00:19:44,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, you didn't?</font>

417
00:19:44,710 --> 00:19:46,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What should we do for lunch?</font>

418
00:19:48,400 --> 00:19:50,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Dad!</font>

419
00:19:50,530 --> 00:19:52,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What did you think of my singing?</font>

420
00:19:52,620 --> 00:19:55,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Ouch, Asa. Stop yanking.</font>

421
00:19:53,100 --> 00:19:55,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Um...</font>

422
00:19:55,980 --> 00:19:58,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess...</font>

423
00:19:58,380 --> 00:20:00,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you stood out.</font>

424
00:20:01,080 --> 00:20:02,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's that mean?</font>

425
00:20:02,300 --> 00:20:04,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She should just lie low.</font>

426
00:20:04,420 --> 00:20:05,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

427
00:20:06,020 --> 00:20:07,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tamashiro-san.</font>

428
00:20:08,960 --> 00:20:11,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She stands out enough as it is.</font>

429
00:20:11,830 --> 00:20:15,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you not like Tamashiro-san?</font>

430
00:20:15,330 --> 00:20:18,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? No, nothing like that.</font>

431
00:20:18,770 --> 00:20:22,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just mean she shouldn't stick 
out for the wrong reasons.</font>

432
00:20:22,400 --> 00:20:25,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Since she's finally not getting bullied.</font>

433
00:20:25,810 --> 00:20:29,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You never know when your 
standing might change.</font>

434
00:20:29,750 --> 00:20:32,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah... You're right.</font>

435
00:20:33,250 --> 00:20:34,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hurry it up, Yoshimura!</font>

436
00:20:35,790 --> 00:20:37,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The upperclassmen 
will let you have it again.</font>

437
00:20:37,900 --> 00:20:40,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it just me, or are they tough on me?</font>

438
00:20:40,780 --> 00:20:42,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's 'cause you're our 
rising star. That's why.</font>

439
00:20:42,930 --> 00:20:44,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whatever.</font>

440
00:20:45,650 --> 00:20:47,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're not auditioning?!</font>

441
00:20:47,490 --> 00:20:49,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nope. I'm not.</font>

442
00:20:49,070 --> 00:20:50,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why not?</font>

443
00:20:50,300 --> 00:20:53,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">'Cause. It's scary standing out.</font>

444
00:20:53,370 --> 00:20:56,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And singing in front of people? No thanks.</font>

445
00:20:56,900 --> 00:20:59,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then why are you in a band?</font>

446
00:20:59,360 --> 00:21:00,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why I chose the bass.</font>

447
00:21:00,810 --> 00:21:03,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Either way, I'm not doing it.</font>

448
00:21:03,630 --> 00:21:07,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aw, and here I thought
 you really had a shot.</font>

449
00:21:07,150 --> 00:21:08,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See you after school.</font>

450
00:21:10,240 --> 00:21:16,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>At the time, I was searching 
and searching far and wide.</i></font>

451
00:21:17,910 --> 00:21:20,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>To the point I got tired of getting mad.</i></font>

452
00:21:22,720 --> 00:21:24,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm thirsty...</font>

453
00:21:26,160 --> 00:21:31,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Should I be giving water 
to my own loneliness?</i></font>

454
00:21:32,280 --> 00:21:34,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Would that help me find it?</i></font>

455
00:21:35,890 --> 00:21:38,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Find what I should be searching for?</i></font>

456
00:21:40,680 --> 00:21:42,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the hell?!</font>

457
00:21:42,730 --> 00:21:45,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How could something like this stand?!</font>

458
00:21:45,710 --> 00:21:46,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Chiyo?</font>

459
00:21:46,990 --> 00:21:50,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So no matter how high I score,</font>

460
00:21:50,420 --> 00:21:53,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I could get rejected just 
for being a girl? Seriously?</font>

461
00:21:53,990 --> 00:22:00,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="10"><font color="#484d50"><b>Uniform Point Deductions for Female Applicants:
Nitto Medical University Accused of Arbitrary Manipulation</b></font></font></font></font>

462
00:21:54,600 --> 00:21:56,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't believe it...</font>

463
00:21:56,880 --> 00:21:59,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How could this have been
 going on all this time?</font>

464
00:22:00,540 --> 00:22:01,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll never let it go...</font>

465
00:22:02,500 --> 00:22:04,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Never! Not ever!</font>

466
00:22:02,940 --> 00:22:04,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Damn. She's really mad.</font>

467
00:22:04,560 --> 00:22:06,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Morimoto's scary, man.</font>

468
00:22:05,580 --> 00:22:08,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I couldn't look away.</i></font>

